# Host canonicalization: www -> non-www (301).
# Requires www.emilybackes.design to be attached as a custom domain on the
# Pages project (otherwise the www host never reaches this file). Cloudflare
# Pages matches the full URL when scheme+host are given; :splat = the matched path.
https://www.emilybackes.design/* https://emilybackes.design/:splat 301

# Dropped experimental pages (not migrated, ~0 traffic) -> journal.
/experimental/* /posts 301

